                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14472806" author="melix" created="Thu, 14 Jun 2012 09:28:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem is related to the fact that &lt;tt&gt;Metadata&lt;/tt&gt; implements &lt;tt&gt;Map&lt;/tt&gt; so the type checker believes we call &lt;/p&gt;
{Metadata.get(&apos;current&apos;)}
&lt;p&gt;. Obviously, in that particular case, it should not think so because it&apos;s a static property.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
